📝 To-Do List Web App

A simple and responsive To-Do List application built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. This project helps users manage daily tasks efficiently by allowing them to add, delete, and mark tasks as complete—all within a clean and intuitive interface.

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add new tasks
- 🗑️ Delete tasks
- ✏️ Mark tasks as complete/incomplete
- 💾 Save tasks using `localStorage` (persistent across sessions)
- 🎨 Light/Dark mode toggle (optional enhancement)
- 📱 Responsive design for desktop and mobile

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML5** – Structure and layout
- **CSS3** – Styling and responsiveness
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – Functionality and DOM manipulation
